race.description: Sky Racing Best 8 Stake Cta Division1
race.comment: HUNTER FRED (7) scored by 1.5 lengths last time (16.71) in a Grade 5 over 300m at Murray Bridge. Has two wins already from this draw. With a clean break looks hard to beat. TOWN STRANGER (1) ran fourth in a OPEN last time, copping a check in the run and finishing 9 lengths from the winner over 400m at Gawler. Has four wins from Box 1. Must include in calculations. STARLIGHT RIOT (5) is a fast dog well performed over the sprint races. Scored over 342m at this track last time in a Grade 2/3/4 (19.57). Strike rate this distance strong having won nine of 10 tries. Bold showing expected again. GRAND CHIEF (8) did a good job to finish third last time out over 400m at Gawler (23.14) in a OPEN, the second top-three finish on the trot.
